                <div class="product-description tabcontent" id="Ingredients">
                    <p><strong>Sea Whip:</strong> The active ingredient gorgonian extract is derived from a marine organism known as sea whip, which is a renewable resource in the Caribbean Sea. Gorgonian extract has powerful anti-irritant and soothing properties. This makes it an excellent ingredient for redness-prone and sensitive skin.</p>

<p><strong>Low Molecular Weight Hyaluronic Acid: </strong>A complex sugar molecule occurring naturally in the body, hyaluronic acid (HA) hydrates by drawing water into the skin. It holds up to 1,000 times its weight in water, and makes skin plumper, softer and smoother. Unlike conventional HA, which tends to sit on top of the skin due to its large molecular size, low molecular weight HA helps to replenish the lost HA in the deeper layers of the skin that occurs during the aging process, which firms and hydrates the skin.</p>

<p><strong>Niacinamide (vitamin B3):</strong> Niacinamide increases ceramide and free fatty acids in the skin, which are key components of its protective lipid barrier. Along with keeping in moisture and boosting hydration, it also calms redness and brightens skin.</p>

<p><strong>Copper Peptide: </strong>A peptide with a high affinity for copper, this ingredient strengthens skin and accelerates repair.</p>

<p><strong>Tetrapeptide-14, Tea Extracts, Boswellia Serrate Extract, Honey:</strong> A mixture of a redness-reducing peptide combined with the antioxidant properties of tea and the soothing qualities of honey and boswellia serrate.&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Aloe: </strong>Extracted from the aloe vera plant, soothing aloe contains amino acids, vitamins and minerals.</p>

